================================================================================
                         MODIFICATION SUMMARY
================================================================================

SafeRelay adds the following features on top of the upstream projects:
- Cloudflare Turnstile human verification
- Union ban system integration
- Local fraud detection database
- White list functionality
- Graphical admin panel (Inline Keyboard)
- Broadcast system with batch processing
- Message statistics tracking
- Rate limiting and spam protection
- Message editing synchronization
- Memory caching layer for performance

